    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>There is an array A of <strong>N</strong> integers with <strong>Q</strong> queries. There are 2 types of queries:</p>\n<p><strong>Type 1:</strong><br>\nIt contains two integers:<br>\nx y <br/>\nThis means increase a[x] by the given y i.e. a[x] becomes a[x]+y.\n</p>\n<p><strong>Type 2:</strong><br>It contains three integers:<br>\nL R parity <br>\nIf parity=1, then you have to output the sum of all the odd elements in the range L to R (L and R inclusive).<br>\nIf parity=0, then you have to output the sum of all the even elements in the range L to R (L and R inclusive).\n\n</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>First line contains two integers <strong>N</strong> and <strong>Q</strong>.<br><br>\nThe second line contains N spaced integers denoting the array A<sub>1</sub>, A<sub>2</sub>, ..., A<sub>n</sub><br><br>\nNext Q lines contains the queries in the form<br>\n1 x val<br>\nOR <br>\n2 L R parity <br>\nwhere 1 or 2 denotes the type of query.\n\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>Output the answer for each query of type 2 on a new line.</p>\n\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b> N,Q,value </b> \u2264 1000000 <b></b></li>\n<li><b>1</b>\u2264<b> type </b>\u22642</li>\n<li><b>1</b>\u2264<b> x </b>\u2264N</li>\n<li><b>1</b>\u2264<b> L </b>\u2264<b> R </b>\u2264<b> N </b></li>\n<li><b>0\u2264</b><b> parity </b>\u2264<b> 1</b></li>\n</ul>\n\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n4 3\n1 2 3 4\n1 3 1\n2 1 3 0\n2 1 4 1\n<b>Output:</b>\n6 <br>1\n</pre>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Explanation</h3>\n<p>After the first query A[3] becomes 4<br>So for the second query answer is 2+4=6<br>Answer for the third query is 1.</p>",
